<chapter xml:id="SecondaryDominants">
    <title>Secondary Dominant Chords</title>
    <introduction>
        <p>So far we have studied <xref ref="DiatonicChordsInMajor" text="title">diatonic harmony</xref> (chords without accidentals, with the exception of the use of raised <scaledeg>6</scaledeg> and <scaledeg>7</scaledeg> in minor, which are considered diatonic). In the following chapters, we will study <em>chromatic</em> harmony.</p>
    </introduction>
